Justin Bieber's penis just broke the internet Justin Bieber's penis just broke the internet 
Press Association 2014 / / National Entertainment News Share 
Justin Bieber fans were given something to get very excited about as naked pictures of the star emerged. 
Photos of the Canadian singer relaxing starkers while on holiday first appeared on the New York Daily News website , but the Bieber wiener was censored out of the images. 
Somehow, though, the uncensored versions emerged on Twitter. 
And the Beliebers are impressed. I thought seeing Lady Gaga on TV would be the biggest pop star moment today but sweet baby Jesus, thank you Justin Bieber 😅😏🍆 
— Calvin Bremer (@calvinbremer) October 7, 2015 Justin Bieber's dick everywhere this is the best day of my life
